{"tid":288480,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"9大醫療專業 2030年料缺人才","createTime":"2017-06-18T08:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T09:10:23.000Z","uid":108039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cec679601ac970256f54875e415144475348d10c","tid":288480,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:25:43.000Z","msg":"【經濟日報專訊】港府委託港大進行的醫療專業人力評估顯示，2030年至少9大工種人手短缺，其中醫生及護士均缺逾千人。當局擬調整學額，並倡輸入海外醫療專業人員。但醫學會指高估醫生短缺，護士協會則認為低估不足。<br />\n<br />\n有保險業代表料醫護人手不足，勢令私營醫療收費進一步飈升，中產有買醫療保險也未必能享受私營醫療服務。<br />\n<br />\n港府委託港大進行、為時5年的醫療人力規劃和專業發展策略檢討完成，研究按本港2015年醫療服務模式及水平，涵蓋未來人口老化、已知社福措施及學額等因素，推算13個醫療專業未來人手需求，發現連同醫護及牙醫在內至少9個醫療專業人手，至2030年將現短缺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/9%E5%A4%A7%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD-2030%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%99%E7%BC%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D-225521082.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F9%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2599%2582%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25A5%25AD-2030%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%2599%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%258D-225521082.html&d=zS8mjHy6ywoVYTmiwIoSbNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a70579b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/9%E5%A4%A7%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD-2030%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%99%E7%BC%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D-225521082.html</a>"},{"pid":"70ea45c10ee0007ec5e0faaccb1b4516d881f431","tid":288480,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:26:59.000Z","msg":"中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27e6cf80b0ddc8dd4f16b4296baa1dc54e3ad53","tid":288480,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163b8005c4b1657a9636ea26d0347f67b380e415","tid":288480,"uid":73722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit